========================================
Welcome to Super Ubuntu Docker Container
========================================
Version: 1.1 (Ubuntu 24.04 LTS base)
Features:
• Zsh with oh-my-zsh
• Tools: git, python3, nodejs (v20), awscli (v2), jq, vim, htop
• Code-server (VS Code v4.107.1) on port 8080 (set ENABLE_CODE_SERVER=true)
• SSH on port 22 (set ENABLE_SSH=true; key auth recommended)
• Persistent data: /home/user/data
• Runs as non-root user 'user' for security
Run 'help' for usage instructions.
Note: Use sudo for privileged commands (password required).
Ready! Your data directory is at: /home/user/data
